  "pages": [
    {
      "type": "patchouli:text",
      "text": "A fundamental large-scale alchemical mechanism. It excites substances to be infused using Mana Sparks and fixes them onto a base form at the athanor pillar."
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:crafting",
      "title": "Athanor Pillar",
      "text": "The core of alchemical machinery used to precisely attach substances to the base form.$(br2)It has durability that withstands high concentration Mana.",
      "recipe": "magitech:athanor_pillar"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:text",
      "title": "Mechanism Overview",
      "text": "Mana Sparks emitted from Mana Nodes excite the infused substances and transport them as particles to the Athanor Pillar.$(br2)The Mana Deexciter Core embedded in the Athanor Pillar deexcites the transported infused substance particles and fixes them to the target location on the base form on the pillar.$(br2)This allows precise infusion of Alchemical Aspects and substances to the desired location."
    },
